<h2>How to Download Rat Race</h2>
Rat Race is currently <strong>in the development stage</strong> <strong>and not available for download yet</strong>. Stay updated by following the game's development blog and joining our Discord community. This will ensure you're the first to know when Rat Race becomes available!
<h3>Gameplay Overview</h3>
Rat Race offers a frantic, tactical multiplayer experience where quick thinking is as vital as strategic planning. Each player controls four animatronics across 20+ dynamic rooms, balancing offensive strategies with crucial defenses. <strong>Sabotage your opponents’ equipment and animatronics</strong> while protecting your own from hacks. Enhance your characters’ abilities through skill trees, but choose wisely—each decision could dramatically alter the course of the game.

All gameplay is hosted on private, secure servers featuring custom anti-cheat measures and cloud-based progress saving. Enjoy the thrill of competition <strong>on a global scale with online</strong> leaderboards, GameJolt integration, Discord Rich Presence, and supported minor modding.

